data.title: America's Best in Norfolk at JANAF Shopping Center
data.meta_description: Get 2 pairs of glasses and an eye exam for $79.95 at America's Best in Norfolk at JANAF Shopping Center. Book online today!
data.text:
About America's Best Contacts & Eyeglasses

JANAF Shopping Center

If you are in Norfolk or any of the surrounding areas, stop in and check out what America's Best Contacts & Eyeglasses offers!

Affordable Glasses in Norfolk

Save big on glasses with our 2 pairs for $79.95 offer. This offer applies to over 100 frames in the store tagged $69.95 with single-vision plastic uncoated lenses!

When you purchase two pairs of glasses, you'll receive a FREE eye exam* ($69 value)!

If you are interested in upgrading your lenses, we offer great savings on all lens options, including high-index lenses (thinner and lighter), polarized, Transitions, and more!

Contact Lens Exam Available

If you need an updated contact lens prescription, we have you covered! Our contact lens exam is only $119, but you can save even more with our exclusive Eyecare Club.

When you join the Eyecare Club, you'll receive 3 years of free contacts exams and discounts on your contact lenses and eyeglasses! Ask an associate for more details.

Norfolk Eye Exam Appointments

Schedule your eye exam with a licensed optometrist today. We offer convenient evening and weekend hours to make it easy for you to book your annual eye exam with one of our eye doctors today.

FIND EXAM TIMES
